2. **Recall**: There is only one mining excavator in the image, and it is localized by a bounding box. There are no other mining excavators or mining trucks visible in the image.
3. **Fit**: The bounding box is neither too loose nor too tight. It fits well around the mining excavator, capturing the entire object without cutting off any significant parts or including too much outside area.
